data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE SAT 10AM*** MULTIGENERATIONAL OPPORTUNITY in this single level near BSU, with an attached 1 bed 1bath, own Living Rm & Kitchen, its own entrance and possibly its own 3rd bay garage. Embrace the main home, recently remodeled with roof in 2022, HVAC in 2021, New ducting and plumbing lines, New kitchen and appliances in 2018 (all appliances have  1 yr warranty), New tile and laminate flooring, New tile backsplash, and granite countertops and copper sinks! Built and owned by the same loving family  nearly 40 years, the Spanish Architecture and Design bring warmth and charm. Low maintenance yard and nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, minutes from walking paths, parks, shopping, dining, & entertainment options, you can't ask for any more. YOUR NEW HOME CHECKS ALL THE BOXES!
